sleepproxyclient (0.6) unstable; urgency=low

  * Fixes lease time handling (Issue #3)
  * Fixes registration on networks with multiple sleep proxy servers (Issue #4)
  * Removed option to specify the devide model since it is not mandatory.
    Use avahi to announce the _device-info._tcp service instead.
 
